    
 ------------------QNIFFT22--------------------------
 * Version 2.2                                            *
 * a program to solve the non-linear P-B equation         *
 * 2 dielectric regions, ionic strength, periodic         *
 * and focussing boundary conditions.                     *
 * Does nonlinear salt analysis                           *
 * uses mike holsts inexact newton method                 *
 * implemented by jonathan hecht, new input style         *
 * and multigridding by kas 6 sept, 1993                  *
 * dielectric smoothing added july 95, kas                *
 * 2nd, site potl. charge file added. Reads atom          *
 * names of form 2H2                                      *
 * charge anti-aliasing added may 96                      *
 * Mixed salt NLPB added Oct 99 by Vinod Misra/KAS        *
 * Mixed salt NLPB doesnt work with channel ionic diffrnce*
 * reduce memory requirements- 7-feb-01                   *
 * cleaned up mkmaps 14-feb-01                            *
 * read radii, charges from *.atm file 10-apr-01          *
 * compute atomic forces               10-apr-01          *
 * output reaction field, potl.        27-apr-01          *
 * improved surface mapping            18-may-01          *
 * include reentrant surface remapping 28-may-01          *
 * added parameter for addtl pdb files rgc 7-aug-12       *
